## Summary

12 gaps identified. The first three (GAP-001 sqrt, GAP-002 log, GAP-003 ulp primitive) are **the immediate Axiom 11 → Axiom 11′ refinement criteria** and have the highest capability spread. GAP-011 (hardened dual-arm probe lifting) is independent of the Axiom 11′ path and has a self-contained transplant story.

